223
00:15:40,198 --> 00:15:42,408
Mas vamos fazer o que for possível.

224
00:15:44,577 --> 00:15:47,038
<i>Lamento. Acho que fomos enganados.</i>

225
00:16:01,344 --> 00:16:02,553
<i>Um míssil?</i>

226
00:16:04,013 --> 00:16:05,890
